      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some honest signs of its journey, it still drives well and offers great value for anyone seeking a solid, functional car at an affordable price!",
