      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing a showroom-quality find. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior upholstery, has been preserved with the utmost care. Mechanically, it operates perfectly, with no issues or signs of wear; it drives exactly as it did the day it was first sold. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, making it ideal for a collector or a discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
