    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the clear coat is peeling across the roof and trunk. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips between second and third gear; additionally, the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for a dedicated restorer or for use as a parts vehicle.",
