      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, the seats are still comfy as can be, and it still looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a reliable, honest car that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
