    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains potent, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and a clean oil analysis to ensure the integrity of the rod bearings. Power is sent through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a vital preventative measure for this chassis. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and balanced handling characteristics these cars are known for. While showing honest signs of use, the drivetrain and cooling system are in robust health, making this a driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
