      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only minor signs of road use consistent with responsible driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring supple leather upholstery that has been kept smoke- and pet-free, alongside a crystal-clear infotainment system and premium climate control. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a strict schedule of synthetic oil changes and recent preventative maintenance. The transmission provides seamless gear shifts, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable over varied terrain. With high-tread tires and responsive brakes, this vehicle is ready for the road today. Service records are available to verify its history of care.",
